      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>the way you look tonight</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Some day, when I'm awfully low,</l>
          <l>When the world is cold,</l>
          <l>I will feel the glow just thinking of you</l>
          <l>And the way you look tonight.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Yes you're lovely, with your smile so warm</l>
          <l>And your cheeks so soft,</l>
          <l>There is nothing for me but to love you,</l>
          <l>And the way you look tonight.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>With each word your tenderness grows</l>
          <l>Tearing my face apart-</l>
          <l>And that laugh that wrinkles your nose,</l>
          <l>It touches my foolish heart.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Lovely, never ever change</l>
          <l>Keep that breathless charm,</l>
          <l>Won't you please arrange it?</l>
          <l>Cause I love you, just the way you look tonight.</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
